- [EMPIRICAL] First study to apply FinBERT sentiment analysis to the entire historical corpus of the Federal Reserve's Beige Book (1970-2025) and construct a regional panel dataset to analyze local economic activity and spillovers. (Significance: MEDIUM; Confidence: 9.0/10)
